    <summary>Multiboot USB and DVD creator</summary>
    <description>
SARDU multiboot creator automates the download and build of a multiboot USB/DVD/CD. Many bootable images are divided into categories; tools, antivirus, utility, Linux, Windows, and user-defined ISO images.

With the Bios Legacy and EFI multiboot support you can boot a PC or a Mac from the pendrive USB and make maintenance, do a virus scan, recover and save data, install Windows from USB, try or install Linux Live.

